if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('WorkOrder')
and type = 'U')
drop table WorkOrder
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: WorkOrder */
/*==============================================================*/
create table WorkOrder (
ID int identity(1,1),
WO_No varchar(12) not null,
ProductNo varchar(12) not null,
OrderNo varchar(12) not null,
OrderNum int not null,
MouldNo varchar(12) not null,
WO_SocketAmount int not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_So__5D2BD0E6 default (1),
WO_Planner varchar(12) not null,
WO_DueDate datetime not null,
WO_OriginalQty int not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Or__5E1FF51F default (0),
WO_Qty int null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Qt__5F141958 default (0),
WO_DoneQty int null,
WO_Priority int null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Pr__60083D91 default (0),
WO_Dalayable bit null,
WO_DalayDay decimal(4, 2) not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Da__60FC61CA default (0),
WO_AheadDay decimal(4, 2) not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Ah__61F08603 default (0),
WO_SchStartDate datetime not null,
WO_SchEndDate datetime not null,
WO_ActualStartDate datetime null,
WO_ActualEndDate datetime null,
WO_Status char(1) null,
WO_DispatchQty int not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Di__62E4AA3C default (0),
WO_DispatchFlag bit not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Di__63D8CE75 default (0),
WO_ApproveFlag varchar(2) not null constraint DF__WorkOrder__WO_Ap__64CCF2AE default (0),
WO_ApprovedBy varchar(12) null,
WO_ApprovedDate datetime null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
constraint PK_WORKORDER primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
